# Renaissance / Dashboard shared boundary

**Canonical doc:** [`docs/architect/policy_wiring_surface_map_v1.md`](docs/architect/policy_wiring_surface_map_v1.md) **§5 Team ownership and shared-boundary protocol**.

**Lock steps:** pull → announce lock (file or surface) → merge → release lock.

**Bright line:** persisted DB / ledger wins for **primary** narrative; recompute only in **labeled** preview or audit. Dashboard: presentation, not truth semantics. Renaissance: Kitchen/policy logic; do not change **`dashboard.html`** without coordination.

**See §5.2–5.3** for the full table (may vs must not) and shared-file list.
